Title: Memorable journey of my life
DateModified: '2019-03-05'
DatePublished: '2019-03-05'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/memorable-journey-of-my-life
SetInCountry: Pakistan
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Hameeda Gul Mohammad
AuthorCountry: Pakistan
Text: This story is about 2 brothers whose belong to a rich family live in hyderabad
  karachi but they did not do journey in local buses of the city because their father
  is fudelist so they decided to visit hyderabad to karachi by local bus.During journey
  they face many problems for example environmental pollution,huge crowd in bus,stuff,traffic
  problems,bus stand at stop for half an hour many thing else so in my story i tell
  reality .I also told how  poor people suffer in this local buses they face crowd
  in the bus and pay huge fair to conductor
